name: Untitled Cell Game
description:
Made with <3 for Brackeys Jam 2021.1 (Stronger together) by a few friends that like making things, but are definitely not what you would consider "professionals" 😆. Unfortunately due to shader restrictions, WebGL is not supported. 

You are a small cell in a large organism, fighting off viruses and inferior cells. But without a collection of trusty organelles surrounding you, you are bound to run out of energy and die, or be unable to produce antibodies to fight. Collect organelles in the environment around you. Make sure to consume tons of nutrients, and fight off your deadly enemies, but be careful not to get to close.

Credits:

- User interface: Tee1er

- Music: SpaceCheddar

- Graphics: Nifley

- Gameplay: SpaceCheddar and Nifley
